<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MacMenuBar.com (中文)</title><link>https://macmenubar.com</link><description>精心整理的1300多款Mac菜单栏应用目录</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 21:32:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>中间</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/middle/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/middle.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Middle" class="resource__image aligncenter wp-image-13524" height="520" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/middle.webp" width="500" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Middle为macOS带来了久违的中键点击支持，让你可以通过直观的触控板或妙控鼠标手势在新标签页中打开链接并触发操作，所有这些功能都集成在一个简单、轻量的工具中。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="button secondary small" href="https://middleclick.app/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 21:32:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>快照状态</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/snapstate/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/snapstate.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="SnapState" class="resource__image aligncenter wp-image-13517" height="260" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/snapstate.webp" width="400" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SnapState 让你可以保存并即时恢复你的 macOS 设置，从窗口位置到浏览器标签页，让切换工作场景不再混乱，而是尽在掌控。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="button secondary small" href="https://getsnapstate.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 08:42:32 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>猫头鹰焦点</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/owlfocus/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/owlfocus-scaled.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="OwlFocus" class="resource__image aligncenter wp-image-13512 size-full" height="1909" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/owlfocus-scaled.webp" width="2560" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OwlFocus通过微妙地模糊非活动窗口来提升您的专注力，保持工作空间整洁宁静。它运行迅速，尊重您的隐私，并能与OpenClaw无缝集成，实现轻松自动化。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="button secondary small" href="https://www.capyapp.dev/owlfocus" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 17:20:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>在线指示器</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/online-indicator/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/online-indicator.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="在线状态指示器" class="resource__image aligncenter wp-image-13347 size-full" height="740" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/online-indicator.webp" width="1080" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Online Indicator 将易于忽略的 Wi-Fi 图标替换为清晰的状态信号，显示您当前是已连接、被阻止还是离线状态。您可以自定义符号、颜色和标签，同时自动 Ping 功能会在后台静默监控您的网络连接。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="button secondary small" href="https://github.com/bornexplorer/OnlineIndicator" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 09:35:09 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>维修站墙</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/pitwall/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/pitwall.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Pitwall" class="resource__image aligncenter wp-image-13334" height="494" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/pitwall.webp" width="400" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pitwall 让一级方程式赛车触手可及，实时显示赛车位置、单圈时间和锦标赛排名，一目了然。它提供干净、原生的 macOS 体验，让车迷能够追踪每一场比赛，同时保持工作空间整洁。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="button secondary small" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/pitwall-live-stats/id6758950790" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 09:34:40 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>